### THREE-SHOT: MITCH, BARTENDER, DONNIE SILHOUETTED BY THE PICTURE WINDOW

A blonde athletic-built twink--DONNIE WYNANT(20's, powder blue capri pants and a pastel-colored "alligator" polo)--stands behind Mitch.

MITCH
(without looking up)
